{
  "type": "doc",
  "content": [
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
        "level": 1
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Proxmox VE中Intel e1000e网卡硬件单元挂起问题终极解决方案"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
        "level": 2
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "概要"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "本文详细介绍了Proxmox VE环境中Intel e1000e系列网卡（I218-LM、I219-V等）出现硬件单元挂起(Hardware Unit Hang)问题的完整解决方案。通过日志分析、问题定位、多种解决策略对比以及验证方法，帮助用户彻底解决网卡导致的系统崩溃问题。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
        "level": 2
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "标签"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "#ProxmoxVE #Intel网卡 #e1000e #硬件单元挂起 #网络故障排除"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
        "level": 2
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "正文"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "在虚拟化环境中，网络稳定性至关重要。然而，许多Proxmox VE用户都曾遇到过一个令人头疼的问题：Intel e1000e系列网卡频繁出现硬件单元挂起错误，导致整个虚拟化平台瘫痪。今天，我将分享一套完整的解决方案，帮助大家彻底解决这个问题。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
        "level": 3
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "问题现象"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "首先，让我们认识一下这个问题的典型表现："
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "bulletList",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "PVE管理界面突然无法访问"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "虚拟机网络中断，无法连接"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "系统日志中频繁出现类似错误："
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "codeBlock",
      "attrs": {
        "language": null
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "kernel: e1000e 0000:00:19.0 eno1: Detected Hardware Unit Hang:\nTDH                  <2a>\nTDT                  <77>\nnext_to_use          <77>\nnext_to_clean        <29>\n"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
        "level": 3
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "问题根因分析"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "经过大量日志分析和实践验证，我们发现这个问题主要源于："
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "orderedList",
      "attrs": {
        "start": 1,
        "type": null
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Intel e1000e驱动与特定网卡型号的兼容性问题"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "硬件卸载功能（TSO/GSO/GRO）在高负载下触发驱动bug"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "校验和卸载功能异常导致数据包处理错误"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
        "level": 3
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "解决方案详解"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
        "level": 4
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "方案一：网络接口配置持久化（推荐）"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "这是最稳定可靠的解决方案："
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "codeBlock",
      "attrs": {
        "language": "bash"
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "# 备份原配置\ncp /etc/network/interfaces /etc/network/interfaces.bak\n\n# 编辑网络配置\nnano /etc/network/interfaces\n"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "在对应网卡配置段添加："
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "codeBlock",
      "attrs": {
        "language": "bash"
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "auto eno1\niface eno1 inet manual\n    post-up /sbin/ethtool -K $IFACE tso off gso off gro off\n    post-up /sbin/ethtool -A $IFACE rx off tx off\n    post-up /sbin/ethtool -K $IFACE tx off rx off\n"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "应用配置："
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "codeBlock",
      "attrs": {
        "language": "bash"
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "systemctl restart networking\n"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
        "level": 4
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "方案二：Systemd服务配置（备用）"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "如果方案一不适用，可以使用Systemd服务："
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "codeBlock",
      "attrs": {
        "language": "bash"
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "cat <<EOF > /etc/systemd/system/disable-offload.service\n[Unit]\nDescription=Disable NIC offloading for e1000e\nAfter=network.target\n\n[Service]\nType=oneshot\nExecStart=/sbin/ethtool -K eno1 tso off gso off gro off rx off tx off\n\n[Install]\nWantedBy=multi-user.target\nEOF\n"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "启用服务："
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "codeBlock",
      "attrs": {
        "language": "bash"
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "systemctl enable --now disable-offload.service\n"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
        "level": 4
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "方案三：驱动参数优化"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "创建驱动配置文件："
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "codeBlock",
      "attrs": {
        "language": "bash"
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "cat <<EOF > /etc/modprobe.d/e1000e.conf\n# 禁用可能引起问题的硬件功能\noptions e1000e InterruptThrottleRate=3000\noptions e1000e RxIntDelay=100\noptions e1000e TxIntDelay=100\noptions e1000e SmartPowerDownEnable=0\noptions e1000e KumeranLockLoss=1\nEOF\n"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "重新加载驱动："
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "codeBlock",
      "attrs": {
        "language": "bash"
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "update-initramfs -u\nreboot\n"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
        "level": 3
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "验证解决方案"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "实施解决方案后，需要验证效果："
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "orderedList",
      "attrs": {
        "start": 1,
        "type": null
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "检查卸载功能状态："
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "codeBlock",
      "attrs": {
        "language": "bash"
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "ethtool -k eno1 | grep -E 'tso|gso|gro'\n"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "orderedList",
      "attrs": {
        "start": 2,
        "type": null
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "监控错误计数："
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "codeBlock",
      "attrs": {
        "language": "bash"
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "ethtool -S eno1 | grep error\n"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "orderedList",
      "attrs": {
        "start": 3,
        "type": null
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "检查内核日志："
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "codeBlock",
      "attrs": {
        "language": "bash"
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "dmesg | grep -i e1000e\n"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
        "level": 3
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "长期监控策略"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "为了确保问题彻底解决，建议设置监控："
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "codeBlock",
      "attrs": {
        "language": "bash"
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "cat <<EOF > /usr/local/bin/monitor-e1000e.sh\n#!/bin/bash\nERROR_COUNT=$(ethtool -S eno1 | grep rx_csum_offload_errors | awk '{print $2}')\nif [ $ERROR_COUNT -gt 0 ]; then\n    echo \"Warning: e1000e errors detected at $(date)\" | logger -t e1000e-monitor\nfi\nEOF\n\nchmod +x /usr/local/bin/monitor-e1000e.sh\necho \"*/10 * * * * /usr/local/bin/monitor-e1000e.sh\" >> /etc/crontab\n"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
        "level": 3
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "替代方案"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "如果软件方案仍无法解决问题，建议："
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "orderedList",
      "attrs": {
        "start": 1,
        "type": null
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "硬件升级：更换为Intel I350、I210等兼容性更好的网卡"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "内核升级：更新到最新版本的Proxmox VE内核"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "驱动手动编译：安装最新版本的Intel e1000e驱动"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
        "level": 3
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "总结"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "通过禁用e1000e网卡的硬件卸载功能，我们可以有效解决硬件单元挂起问题。推荐使用网络接口配置持久化方案，确保配置在重启后依然有效。如果问题持续存在，硬件升级是最彻底的解决方案。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "记住，网络稳定性是虚拟化环境的基础，解决这类底层问题对保障业务连续性至关重要。希望这个解决方案能帮助到遇到同样问题的朋友们。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "horizontalRule"
    },
    {
